             was again indicted<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="180502200048"></xptr>for <rs id="t18050220-57-off339" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18050220-57-off339" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050220-57-off339" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050220-57-cd340" type="crimeDate">14th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050220-57-off339 t18050220-57-cd340"></join>, ten shawls, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050220-57-victim556" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Kyle
                  <interp inst="t18050220-57-victim556" type="surname" value="Kyle"></interp>
