                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050220-57-defend554 t18050220-57-punish344"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Le Blanc.</p>
